OL,6,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC) has
OL,7,Freleased its findings following
OL,8,Finspections of urgent and emergency
OL,9,Fservices, medical services, and
OL,10,Fsurgery at University Hospitals
OL,11,FBirmingham NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,13,FThe trust manages Birmingham
OL,14,FHeartlands Hospital, the Queen
OL,15,FElizabeth Hospital Birmingham,
OL,16,FSolihull Hospital, and Good Hope
OL,17,FHospital.
