OL,3,CCQC publishes inspection report on
OL,4,Chospitals trust
OL,6,FThe inspection was prompted by
OL,7,Fconcerns raised about the quality of
OL,8,Fthe three services inspected. Upon
OL,9,Freview, the concerns were found to be
OL,10,Funfounded.
OL,12,FRatings summary:
OL,14,FUrgent and emergency services at
OL,15,FSolihull Hospital
OL,17,FRated Good overall. This includes
OL,18,Fspecific ratings of Good for being
OL,19,Fsafe, effective, caring, responsive,
OL,20,Fand well-led. This was the first
OL,21,Finspection of the service.
