OL,3,CCQC publishes inspection report on
OL,4,Chospitals trust
OL,6,FCharlotte Rudge, CQC Deputy Director
OL,7,Fof Operations in the Midlands, noted:
OL,8,F"When we inspected University
OL,9,FHospitals Birmingham NHS Foundation
OL,10,FTrust, we found staff who put people
OL,11,Ffirst to deliver the best possible
OL,12,Fcare. Whilst improvements were needed
OL,13,Fin some areas, we saw managers putting
OL,14,Fimprovement plans in place, mitigating
OL,15,Frisks and learning from incidents.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
