OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F371A1732454101
OL,3,CCQC publishes inspection report on
OL,4,Chospitals trust
OL,6,F"In surgery, people told us the level
OL,7,Fof care they'd received was excellent
OL,8,Fand that all staff were responsive,
OL,9,Fcaring and helpful. However, there
OL,10,Fwere frequent staff shortages with
OL,11,Fsome staff saying they felt care was
OL,12,Funsafe as a result. Managers took
OL,13,Fappropriate steps to address vacancies
OL,14,Fwith the resources they had available,
OL,15,Fand recruitment was ongoing.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
