OL,3,CCQC publishes inspection report on
OL,4,Chospitals trust
OL,6,F"In urgent and emergency services,
OL,7,Fpeople were usually seen within four
OL,8,Fhours and staff acted quickly if
OL,9,Fsomeone was at risk of deterioration.
OL,10,FStaff worked effectively in a
OL,11,Fmultidisciplinary team to discuss and
OL,12,Fimprove people's care, and a therapy
OL,13,Fteam was available for people needing
OL,14,Fsupport once they returned home.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
