OL,3,CCQC publishes inspection report on
OL,4,Chospitals trust
OL,6,F"In medical services, people spoke
OL,7,Fpositively and passionately about the
OL,8,Fcare they received. Leaders were
OL,9,Fpresent on the wards and staff felt
OL,10,Fcomfortable raising concerns with
OL,11,Fthem. Staff were delivering person-
OL,12,Fcentred care on the wards we visited
OL,13,Fand involving people in their own care
OL,14,Fto ensure they understood their
OL,15,Fcondition and treatment plans.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
